properties.Name: EquifaxConsumerAccountDesignatorType
properties.Description:
Account Designator indicates if the listed account is joint or individual. 

Undesignated means it is unknown whether the listed account is joint or individual.

Ex:
- Individual
- Joint
- Undesignated
